</group>

textfsm_template:
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value CTS_MODE (\S+)
Value POLICY_STATUS (\S+)
Value IP4_TRUSTS (\S+)
Value IP4_IN_ACL (\S+)
Value IP4_OUT_ACL (\S+)
Value DEVICE_ID (.+)
Value ENCRYPTED_PACKETS (\d+)
Value DECRYPTED_PACKETS (\d+)

Start
  ^CTS\sInterface:\s${INTERFACE}\s*$$
  ^\s*CTS\sis\senabled,\smode\sis\s${CTS_MODE},.*$$
  ^\s*Policy\sstatus\sis\s${POLICY_STATUS},.*$$
  ^\s*IPv4\strusts:\s${IP4_TRUSTS}.*$$
  ^\s*IPv4\singress\saccess\slist:\s${IP4_IN_ACL}\s*$$
  ^\s*IPv4\segress\saccess\slist:\s${IP4_OUT_ACL}\s*$$
  ^\s*Device\sID\sCDP:\s${DEVICE_ID}\s*$$
  ^\s*Monitor\smode:.*$$
  ^\s*CTS\sstatistics:\s${ENCRYPTED_PACKETS}\s+packets\sencrypted,.*$$
  ^\s*${DECRYPTED_PACKETS}\s+packets\sdecrypted\s*$$ -> Record
